58 def signedSquare(val):
59  if val > 0:
60  sign = 1
61  else:
62  sign = -1
63  return val * val * sign

488 class StatusHistory:
489  def __init__(self, max_length=10):
490  self.max_length = max_length
491  self.buffer = []
492 
493  def add(self, status):
494  self.buffer.append(status)
495  if len(self.buffer) > self.max_length:
496  self.buffer = self.buffer[1 : self.max_length + 1]
497 
498  def all(self, proc):
499  for status in self.buffer:
500  if not proc(status):
501  return False
502  return True
503 
504  def latest(self):
505  if len(self.buffer) > 0:
506  return self.buffer[-1]
507  else:
508  return None
509 
510  def length(self):
511  return len(self.buffer)
512 
513  def new(self, status, attr):
514  if len(self.buffer) == 0:
515  return getattr(status, attr)
516  else:
517  return getattr(status, attr) and not getattr(self.latest(), attr)

520 class MoveitJoy:
521  def parseSRDF(self):
522  ri = RobotInterface("/robot_description")
523  planning_groups = {}
524  for g in ri.get_group_names():
525  self.planning_groups_tips[g] = ri.get_group_joint_tips(g)
526  if len(self.planning_groups_tips[g]) > 0:
527  planning_groups[g] = [
528  "/rviz/moveit/move_marker/goal_" + l
529  for l in self.planning_groups_tips[g]
530  ]
531  for name in planning_groups.keys():
532  print(name, planning_groups[name])
533  self.planning_groups = planning_groups
534  self.planning_groups_keys = list(
535  planning_groups.keys()
536  ) # we'd like to store the 'order'
537  self.frame_id = ri.get_planning_frame()
538 
539  def __init__(self):
540  self.initial_poses = {}
541  self.planning_groups_tips = {}
542  self.tf_listener = tf.TransformListener()
543  self.marker_lock = threading.Lock()
544  self.prev_time = rospy.Time.now()
545  self.counter = 0
546  self.history = StatusHistory(max_length=10)
547  self.pre_pose = PoseStamped()
548  self.pre_pose.pose.orientation.w = 1
549  self.current_planning_group_index = 0
550  self.current_eef_index = 0
551  self.initialize_poses = False
552  self.initialized = False
553  self.parseSRDF()
554  self.plan_group_pub = rospy.Publisher(
555  "/rviz/moveit/select_planning_group", String, queue_size=5
556  )
557  self.updatePlanningGroup(0)
558  self.updatePoseTopic(0, False)
559  self.joy_pose_pub = rospy.Publisher("/joy_pose", PoseStamped, queue_size=1)
560  self.plan_pub = rospy.Publisher("/rviz/moveit/plan", Empty, queue_size=5)
561  self.execute_pub = rospy.Publisher("/rviz/moveit/execute", Empty, queue_size=5)
562  self.update_start_state_pub = rospy.Publisher(
563  "/rviz/moveit/update_start_state", Empty, queue_size=5
564  )
565  self.update_goal_state_pub = rospy.Publisher(
566  "/rviz/moveit/update_goal_state", Empty, queue_size=5
567  )
568  self.interactive_marker_sub = rospy.Subscriber(
569  "/rviz_moveit_motion_planning_display/robot_interaction_interactive_marker_topic/update_full",
570  InteractiveMarkerInit,
571  self.markerCB,
572  queue_size=1,
573  )
574  self.sub = rospy.Subscriber("/joy", Joy, self.joyCB, queue_size=1)
575 
576  def updatePlanningGroup(self, next_index):
577  if next_index >= len(self.planning_groups_keys):
578  self.current_planning_group_index = 0
579  elif next_index < 0:
580  self.current_planning_group_index = len(self.planning_groups_keys) - 1
581  else:
582  self.current_planning_group_index = next_index
583  next_planning_group = None
584  try:
585  next_planning_group = self.planning_groups_keys[
586  self.current_planning_group_index
587  ]
588  except IndexError:
589  msg = "Check if you started movegroups. Exiting."
590  rospy.logfatal(msg)
591  raise rospy.ROSInitException(msg)
592  rospy.loginfo("Changed planning group to " + next_planning_group)
593  self.plan_group_pub.publish(next_planning_group)
594 
595  def updatePoseTopic(self, next_index, wait=True):
596  planning_group = self.planning_groups_keys[self.current_planning_group_index]
597  topics = self.planning_groups[planning_group]
598  if next_index >= len(topics):
599  self.current_eef_index = 0
600  elif next_index < 0:
601  self.current_eef_index = len(topics) - 1
602  else:
603  self.current_eef_index = next_index
604  next_topic = topics[self.current_eef_index]
605 
606  rospy.loginfo(
607  "Changed controlled end effector to "
608  + self.planning_groups_tips[planning_group][self.current_eef_index]
609  )
610  self.pose_pub = rospy.Publisher(next_topic, PoseStamped, queue_size=5)
611  if wait:
612  self.waitForInitialPose(next_topic)
613  self.current_pose_topic = next_topic
614 
615  def markerCB(self, msg):
616  try:
617  self.marker_lock.acquire()
618  if not self.initialize_poses:
619  return
620  self.initial_poses = {}
621  for marker in msg.markers:
622  if marker.name.startswith("EE:goal_"):
623  # resolve tf
624  if marker.header.frame_id != self.frame_id:
625  ps = PoseStamped(header=marker.header, pose=marker.pose)
626  try:
627  transformed_pose = self.tf_listener.transformPose(
628  self.frame_id, ps
629  )
630  self.initial_poses[marker.name[3:]] = transformed_pose.pose
631  except (
632  tf.LookupException,
633  tf.ConnectivityException,
634  tf.ExtrapolationException,
635  e,
636  ):
637  rospy.logerr("tf error when resolving tf: %s" % e)
638  else:
639  self.initial_poses[
640  marker.name[3:]
641  ] = marker.pose # tf should be resolved
642  finally:
643  self.marker_lock.release()
644 
645  def waitForInitialPose(self, next_topic, timeout=None):
646  counter = 0
647  while not rospy.is_shutdown():
648  counter = counter + 1
649  if timeout and counter >= timeout:
650  return False
651  try:
652  self.marker_lock.acquire()
653  self.initialize_poses = True
654  topic_suffix = next_topic.split("/")[-1]
655  if topic_suffix in self.initial_poses:
656  self.pre_pose = PoseStamped(pose=self.initial_poses[topic_suffix])
657  self.initialize_poses = False
658  return True
659  else:
660  rospy.logdebug(self.initial_poses.keys())
661  rospy.loginfo(
662  "Waiting for pose topic of '%s' to be initialized", topic_suffix
663  )
664  rospy.sleep(1)
665  finally:
666  self.marker_lock.release()
667 
668  def joyCB(self, msg):
669  if len(msg.axes) == 27 and len(msg.buttons) == 19:
670  status = PS3WiredStatus(msg)
671  elif len(msg.axes) == 8 and len(msg.buttons) == 11:
672  status = XBoxStatus(msg)
673  elif len(msg.axes) == 20 and len(msg.buttons) == 17:
674  status = PS3Status(msg)
675  elif len(msg.axes) == 14 and len(msg.buttons) == 14:
676  status = PS4Status(msg)
677  elif len(msg.axes) == 8 and len(msg.buttons) == 13:
678  status = PS4WiredStatus(msg)
679  else:
680  raise Exception("Unknown joystick")
681  self.run(status)
682  self.history.add(status)
683 
684  def computePoseFromJoy(self, pre_pose, status):
685  new_pose = PoseStamped()
686  new_pose.header.frame_id = self.frame_id
687  new_pose.header.stamp = rospy.Time(0.0)
688  # move in local
689  dist = (
690  status.left_analog_y * status.left_analog_y
691  + status.left_analog_x * status.left_analog_x
692  )
693  scale = 200.0
694  x_diff = signedSquare(status.left_analog_y) / scale
695  y_diff = signedSquare(status.left_analog_x) / scale
696  # z
697  if status.L2:
698  z_diff = 0.005
699  elif status.R2:
700  z_diff = -0.005
701  else:
702  z_diff = 0.0
703  if self.history.all(lambda s: s.L2) or self.history.all(lambda s: s.R2):
704  z_scale = 4.0
705  else:
706  z_scale = 2.0
707  local_move = numpy.array((x_diff, y_diff, z_diff * z_scale, 1.0))
708  q = numpy.array(
709  (
710  pre_pose.pose.orientation.x,
711  pre_pose.pose.orientation.y,
712  pre_pose.pose.orientation.z,
713  pre_pose.pose.orientation.w,
714  )
715  )
716  xyz_move = numpy.dot(tf.transformations.quaternion_matrix(q), local_move)
717  new_pose.pose.position.x = pre_pose.pose.position.x + xyz_move[0]
718  new_pose.pose.position.y = pre_pose.pose.position.y + xyz_move[1]
719  new_pose.pose.position.z = pre_pose.pose.position.z + xyz_move[2]
720  roll = 0.0
721  pitch = 0.0
722  yaw = 0.0
723  DTHETA = 0.005
724  if status.L1:
725  if self.history.all(lambda s: s.L1):
726  yaw = yaw + DTHETA * 2
727  else:
728  yaw = yaw + DTHETA
729  elif status.R1:
730  if self.history.all(lambda s: s.R1):
731  yaw = yaw - DTHETA * 2
732  else:
733  yaw = yaw - DTHETA
734  if status.up:
735  if self.history.all(lambda s: s.up):
736  pitch = pitch + DTHETA * 2
737  else:
738  pitch = pitch + DTHETA
739  elif status.down:
740  if self.history.all(lambda s: s.down):
741  pitch = pitch - DTHETA * 2
742  else:
743  pitch = pitch - DTHETA
744  if status.right:
745  if self.history.all(lambda s: s.right):
746  roll = roll + DTHETA * 2
747  else:
748  roll = roll + DTHETA
749  elif status.left:
750  if self.history.all(lambda s: s.left):
751  roll = roll - DTHETA * 2
752  else:
753  roll = roll - DTHETA
754  diff_q = tf.transformations.quaternion_from_euler(roll, pitch, yaw)
755  new_q = tf.transformations.quaternion_multiply(q, diff_q)
756  new_pose.pose.orientation.x = new_q[0]
757  new_pose.pose.orientation.y = new_q[1]
758  new_pose.pose.orientation.z = new_q[2]
759  new_pose.pose.orientation.w = new_q[3]
760  return new_pose
761 
762  def run(self, status):
763  if not self.initialized:
764  # when not initialized, we will force to change planning_group
765  while True:
766  self.updatePlanningGroup(self.current_planning_group_index)
767  planning_group = self.planning_groups_keys[
768  self.current_planning_group_index
769  ]
770  topics = self.planning_groups[planning_group]
771  next_topic = topics[self.current_eef_index]
772  if not self.waitForInitialPose(next_topic, timeout=3):
773  rospy.logwarn(
774  "Unable to initialize planning group "
775  + planning_group
776  + ". Trying different group."
777  )
778  rospy.logwarn(
779  "Is 'Allow External Comm.' enabled in Rviz? Is the 'Query Goal State' robot enabled?"
780  )
781  else:
782  rospy.loginfo("Initialized planning group")
783  self.initialized = True
784  self.updatePoseTopic(self.current_eef_index)
785  return
786  # Try to initialize with different planning group
787  self.current_planning_group_index += 1
788  if self.current_planning_group_index >= len(self.planning_groups_keys):
789  self.current_planning_group_index = 0 # reset loop
790  if self.history.new(status, "select"): # increment planning group
791  self.updatePlanningGroup(self.current_planning_group_index + 1)
792  self.current_eef_index = 0 # force to reset
793  self.updatePoseTopic(self.current_eef_index)
794  return
795  elif self.history.new(status, "start"): # decrement planning group
796  self.updatePlanningGroup(self.current_planning_group_index - 1)
797  self.current_eef_index = 0 # force to reset
798  self.updatePoseTopic(self.current_eef_index)
799  return
800  elif self.history.new(status, "triangle"):
801  self.updatePoseTopic(self.current_eef_index + 1)
802  return
803  elif self.history.new(status, "cross"):
804  self.updatePoseTopic(self.current_eef_index - 1)
805  return
806  elif self.history.new(status, "square"): # plan
807  rospy.loginfo("Plan")
808  self.plan_pub.publish(Empty())
809  return
810  elif self.history.new(status, "circle"): # execute
811  rospy.loginfo("Execute")
812  self.execute_pub.publish(Empty())
813  return
814  self.marker_lock.acquire()
815  pre_pose = self.pre_pose
816  new_pose = self.computePoseFromJoy(pre_pose, status)
817  now = rospy.Time.from_sec(time.time())
818  # placement.time_from_start = now - self.prev_time
819  if (now - self.prev_time).to_sec() > 1 / 30.0:
820  # rospy.loginfo(new_pose)
821  self.pose_pub.publish(new_pose)
822  self.joy_pose_pub.publish(new_pose)
823  self.prev_time = now
824  # sync start state to the real robot state
825  self.counter = self.counter + 1
826  if self.counter % 10:
827  self.update_start_state_pub.publish(Empty())
828  self.pre_pose = new_pose
829  self.marker_lock.release()
830  # update self.initial_poses
831  self.marker_lock.acquire()
832  self.initial_poses[self.current_pose_topic.split("/")[-1]] = new_pose.pose
833  self.marker_lock.release()
